test_list_of_primes:
assert [2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, ...] == [2, 2]
  Left contains 8 more items, first extra item: 2
  Full diff:
  - [2, 2]
  + [2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2, 2]
test_result_order:
assert [2, 2, 3, 271] == [2, 3]

  Left contains 2 more items, first extra item: 3
  Full diff:
  - [2, 3]
  + [2, 2, 3, 271]
